

**Mo haschu g Jesus ha mashcham ab amjed g hoꞌigeꞌidahuna **

*An g neid g Matthew 6:9-13; 7:7-11 *

1 Sh am hu hebai e hoꞌigeꞌidahun g Jesus ch am i kuhgit. Sh hema hab kaij g chuhchaij ab wui, “T‑kownalig, oi g hig t‑mashcham matt has masma wo t‑hoꞌigeꞌidahu hab masma mo wa g John ha mashcham hegam mo ab si wecho e mashcham.” 

2 Sh hab kaij g Jesus ab ha wui, “Id amt hab wo chei am e hoꞌigeꞌidahunch: 

Jiosh t‑ohg, ab ach si has m‑elid ch si haꞌichuchud g m‑chehgig ch tatchua mapt wo i geꞌedaj g e‑kownaltalig ia t‑shahgid. 

3 Ab g i s‑t‑hoꞌigeꞌid k ab wo t‑mahkad g haꞌichu hugi wehs tashkaj. 

4 Gam g hu hab i juhni g pi ap t‑chuꞌijig nach pi ahchim gam hu pi chechegitod g ha‑chuꞌijig hegam mat hedai i pi ap has chuꞌi ab t‑wui. 

Pi g am hiwgid g Jiawul mas am wo t‑shul pi apꞌekam ch ed.” 

5-6 Sh hab ep kaij g Jesus ab ha wui hegam mo ab si wecho e mashcham, “Neh, tp hems hema pi am hu geꞌe wo haꞌichu hugik. T am hema mehkjed wo jiwia hudunk ab mat ab i chehgim. Kut am wo hih g kihkam e‑hugid am kihkam wui k ab wo haꞌi tai g sismito mat wo gegos g e‑nawoj. 

7 “T hab haha wabsh wo chum chei g hugidaj am kihkam, ‘Pi g ia hu ni‑kudut. Heki ant hu ab yahwidad g ni‑kihjeg. Kutt heki hu wohpiwua g t‑aꞌaliga ha wehm. Nt pi wo i wamig k wo m‑mah haꞌichu.’ 

8 “T wabshaba pi has wo e elid k ab wabsh wo kia tahnid. T am haha wo i wamig k ab wo mah nat pi pi haꞌasa ab wo tahnid. 

9-10 “Pegih, mt ahpim hab wa masma pi haꞌasa ab wo tahnid g Jiosh mam haschu i tatchua. T ab wo em‑mah. Am g wo haꞌichu i e gahgidad. T wo em‑chehgi. Ab g wo shontpag g kihjeg. T ab wo i e kuhpiꞌo em‑wehhejed. 

11 “Neh, s‑mahch am mat pi hedai wabsh g wamad ab wo mah g e‑alidag mat g watopi ab wo tai. 12 Kut pi wabsh g nakshel ab wo mah mat g chuchul nonha ab wo tai. 13 Mam has i masma pi apꞌe ch wabshaba s‑mahch mamt g s‑kehg haꞌichu ab wo ha mah g e‑aꞌaliga. No hig pi g em‑ohg Jiosh baꞌich i e nahtokch mat ab wo ha mah g Hekia S‑apꞌekam Gewkdag hegam mat ab wo tai.” 

**Mash g Jesus g Jiawul wehm ab aꞌai e cheggia **

*An g neid g Matthew 12:22-30; Mark 3:20-27 *

14 Sh am hu hebai hema pi ha neok g cheoj nash pi g jiawul an uꞌukch. Kutsh g Jesus gam hu hab i juh g jiawul. Tsh am ha hekaj i neo. Tsh g hemajkam si has i el. 15 Sh eda haꞌi hab kaij, “Moki g jijawul ha‑geꞌejig ab mahkch g gewkdag. K heg hekaj gam hu hab i ha wua g jijawul ab ha amjed hegam mo an ha uꞌukch.” 16 Sh haꞌijj wabsh chum heki s‑himchudamk g Jesus ch ab chehani mat g s‑hasig haꞌichu hab wo juh k hekaj am wo ha chehgi mo ab Jiosh t amjed. 

17 Sh wabshaba g Jesus s‑mahch mo haschu am chegito ch hab kaij ab ha wui, “S‑mahch am mat g oꞌodham wo padch g hejel e‑jewedga mat ab aꞌai wo e cheggia. Kut g e‑wehm kihkam hab waꞌap wo padch g hejel e‑kihdag mat ab aꞌai wo e cheggia. 18 Pegih, t has hig masma g Jiawul pi wo padch g hejel e‑kownaltalig matp ab wo sha ni‑mah g gewkdag mant am wo i ha wuwhas g piongaj? 19 Neh, em‑pionag o hab waꞌap i ha wuwhasid g jijawul. Kum eda pi hab masma hab ha elid mo g Jiawul ab ha mahkch g gewkdag. Pegih, idam at wo em‑ahgi mo pi woho hegai mam hab chum elid. 20 Jiosh gewkdagkaj ani gam hu hab i ha wua g jijawul. K id am wohokamchud mat heki hu in i wuhsh g Jiosh kownaltalig em‑shahgid. 

21 “Nat hig pi wo e nahtokch g si s‑gegoki kownal g e‑cheggiakudkaj mat wo nuhkud g e‑kih. T hab pi hedai wo wohppoꞌi g haꞌichu enigaj. 22 Tp wabshaba g baꞌich i s‑gegoki kownal wo cheggia k wo gewito k gam hu wo i ui hegai cheggiakudaj mo ab chum si hiwig k am wo aꞌai i tahp g haꞌichu enigaj am ha wehhejed g e‑shondalig. Neh, bani wa masma cheggia g ge Jiawul. 23 K hegam mat hedai pi ab hu wo i ni‑wehmajk ab ni‑wui gegok ch wabsh ha gantan hegam mani s‑ha doꞌibiamk.” 

**Mat g jiawul has masma an uhpam ep wo bei g oꞌodham **

*An g neid g Matthew 12:43-45 *

24 Kush hab ep kaij g Jesus, “Matp hems g jiawul an wo hema uꞌukch g oꞌodham ch wabsh wo dagito mat am hebai ep wo e ul. Kut hegai oꞌodham wo i chum kegch g e‑doakag. T wabshaba g jiawul pi hebai wo chehg k hekaj hab wo i e ah, ‘Mo hig woho d ni‑kih hegai oꞌodham. Nt hig am uhpam wo hih wui.’ 25 Kut wa woho am uhpam wo him k wo cheh mo am wabsh jeg ch si kegchudas ch hehosimhunas. 26 T am haha wo him k wewaꞌak ep wo ha uꞌapa g jijawul. T idam baꞌich wo i pi apꞌek ch am wehmaj wo i chiwia. Neh, t ihda oꞌodham hahawa baꞌich wo i pi apꞌek mo wa ga hu i heki hu.” 

**Mo haschu d s‑wohom s‑hehgig **

27 Sh an wehgaj gegok g hemajkam. Kush hema g uwi hab kaij am wui g Jesus, “Do si geꞌe s‑hehgig heg wehhejed uwi mat an m‑mahsid k m‑siꞌichudahim.” 

28 Sh wabshaba hab kaij g Jesus, “Baꞌich at wo i s‑hehgigk hegam mat ab wo kaihamad g Jiosh haꞌichu ahga.” 

**Mamsh s‑neidamk g s‑hasig haꞌichu **

*An g neid g Matthew 12:38-42 *

29 Sh am i muꞌidahim g hemajkam. Kush hab kaij g Jesus, “Muꞌijj o g ha‑chegitoidag pi apꞌe. K heg hekaj s‑neidamk mant hab wo juh g s‑hasig haꞌichu k am wo wohokamch mani ab Jiosh amjed. Bant waꞌi masma am wo ha chehgi mani d Jiosh si Kehsha matsh wa hab e juh hegai kelibad Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam mash d Jonah. 30 Heg atsh wa am si has masma i e chehgi ha wui g Ninevah t am hemajkam. Nt ahni am si has masma wo i ni‑chehgi am ha wui g hemajkam iaꞌi idani. 

31-32 “Hegam Ninevah t am hemajkam atsh gam hu s‑ohhod g pi ap e‑chegitoi am i kahk g Jonabad k hab pi ab hu wo e chuꞌijigch geꞌe lodaita tash ch ed. Ni ahni baꞌich d i si haꞌichu mo g Jonabad. Kum eda pi ab hu ni‑kaiham ch heg hekaj ab wo motoig g chuꞌijig lodaita tash ch ed. \(31\) Mehkjed atsh ab i hih g uwi kownal ab wakolim tahgio amjed mat ab wo kaiha g Solomonbad haꞌichu mahchig. Ni ahni baꞌich d i si haꞌichu mo g Solomonbad. Kum eda pi ab hu ni‑kaiham ch heg hekaj ab wo motoig g chuꞌijig lodaita tash ed.” 

**Mash em‑tonlidch g em‑amichudadag **

*An g neid g Matthew 5:15; 6:22-23 *

33 Kush hab ep kaij g Jesus, “Wohokam o wepogidas mo g lahmpa. Kum s‑mahch mo pi hab d ahga g lahmpa mas am wo e ehsto haꞌichu wecho. Mt an wo dai mat hebai wo ha tonlidad hegam mo ab i wahpk. 

34 “Em‑wuhpui at s‑ap am wo i wahki g tonlig matp wo s‑mamsk k wabshaba pi am hu wo i wahki matp pi wo mamsk. Kum heg hekaj s‑ap ha nuhkud. 35 Pegih, wahm amt wo si s‑ap nuhkudad g haꞌichu e‑amichudadag mat heg s‑ap am wo i wahki g wohokam. 36 Bat waꞌi masma ab wo i shuhdad g em‑chegitoidag g wohokam.” 

**Matsh g Jesus ab haꞌichu ha abch hegam mo d Palasi ch hegam ehp mo d chehanig ha mashchamdam **

*An g neid g Matthew 23:1-36; Mark 12:38-40 *

37 Tsh am i haꞌasa neo g Jesus. Tsh am hema jiwia g Palasi k am waid mat wo wehmaj e gegos. Kutsh wa woho am i wahk k am i dahiwua matsh wo e gegos. 38 Tsh hegai Palasi si has i el neidok mat pi e wako hab masma mo d ha himdag. 

39 Kush s‑amichud g Jesus ch hab kaij ab wui, “Neh, ahpim Palasi am si kegchud g e‑honshpadag. K wabshaba g em‑chegitoi wabsh shuhdags g pi apꞌekamkaj. Heg o wa wepo mam an waꞌi wehgaj si kegchud g hohas‑hahaꞌa. K ged hu ha eda wabsh kia s‑bibtagi. 40 Damt wabsh wo totontok mamtp heg wo waꞌi s‑ap nuhkud e‑honshpadag. Jiosh at hab waꞌap nahto g em‑doakag. Kumt heg ep wo chum nuhkud. 41 Am g wehs wo i dagito Jiosh wui k hab wo s‑chechojimak ab shoꞌigkam ha wui ch wo nei mat wehs haꞌichu wo s‑kehgajk am em‑wehhejed. 

42 “Neh, ahpim Palasi am ab mahk g Jiosh g hemako tahpani mo wehst‑mahm e tahpanch g em‑eniga, chum hems g nahnko mahs pi‑miandi ch haꞌichu tatk. T wabshaba g Jiosh s‑koꞌokam wo em‑namkid nam pi pi apꞌechud hegai mam haschukaj ha shoꞌigchud haꞌi ch pi ab hu tatchua g Jiosh. 43 Shaꞌam waꞌi s‑hohhoꞌid mamt si s‑apko wo dadhaiwua am cheopi ch ed ch s‑hohhoꞌid mat ab wo si has em‑elidad g hemajkam mamt an wo i wuwha kahya ch ed. 44 Ih, shoꞌig\! Mt wo si s‑koꞌokam e namkidach. Neh, pi at wo mahsk g hihaꞌini matp pi am hu wo tohnkdask. Kumtp hems am wabsh dahm wo oiopod. Pegih, bat sha masma pi wo mahchk g hemajkam mam d pi apꞌekam nam pi ehstokch g pi ap e‑chuꞌijig.” 

45 Kush hema hab kaij g chehanig ha mashchamdam ab wui, “Ha mashchamdam, ahchim ap hab waꞌap has t‑ahg hab kaijch.” 

46 Sh hab kaij g Jesus, “Pegih, ab em‑wui o hab waꞌap him g s‑koꞌok em‑namkidadag. Muꞌi s‑hasig haꞌichu am ab ha chehani g hemajkam. K id d s‑wehch haꞌichu mohtoi am ha wehhejed. M eda ahpim pi haꞌichu hab shaꞌi wua mams hekaj ha wehm wo moht. 

47-48 “Em‑shohshon at muꞌi ha kokda g Jiosh haꞌichu i tashogiddam. Kum ahpim ha wepo masma, chum ams ha hehosid g ha‑hihaꞌiniga hegam mamt ha kokda. K heg hekaj ab em‑wui him g s‑koꞌok em‑namkidadag. 49 Heki o hu hab kaij g Jiosh, ‘Ab ant wo i ha wuwhas g haꞌichu i tashogiddam ha shahgid g hemajkam. Kut haꞌi wo ha‑kokda k haꞌi wo ha shoꞌigch.’ 50 Neh, kum ha wepo chuꞌijig mamtp ha wepo haꞌichu elid. Kut wepo masma wo em‑ai g s‑koꞌok ha‑namkidadag heg hekaj wehs mat hab juh ga hu i amjed mat in i e nahto g jewed. 51 Abelbad atsh wa wehpeg e muhkid. Tsh amjed muꞌi ep e koꞌij. Tsh g Zecariabad ga hu si ha oidch e muhkid amai shahgid g iagchulidakud ch geꞌe cheopi. Kum ahpim ha wepo chuꞌijig hegam matsh wa ha kokda ch ha wepo masma wo bei g s‑koꞌok e‑namkidadag mamtp hedai ha wepo elid haꞌichu. 

52 “Ahpim chehanig ha mashchamdam amt wo i chum ha amichudach g hemajkam mat has masma wo s‑mahchk g Jiosh. Kum eda ahpim pi mahch ch ep ha shohbidch hegam mo s‑mahchimk. Heg o wa wepo mam ab yahwidad g kihjeg mat pi hedai am hu wo i wah. Jiosh at s‑koꞌokam wo em‑namkid heg hekaj.” 

53 Tsh am i wuhsh g Jesus k gam hu chum hih. Tsh hegam chehanig ha mashchamdam ch Palasi ab hahawa si s‑ta keꞌidam has ahg k muꞌi haꞌichu kakke 54 hab wabsh chum ahgch mat wo heki himch mat pi ap haꞌichu hab wo chei. 

